Abstract = {To promote graduate students' active learning, deep reading of high
   quality papers was done by graduate students enrolled in biochemistry
   and microbiology pharmacy curriculum offered by college of life science,
   Jiangxi Normal University from 2013 to 2015. The number of graduate
   students, who participated in the course in 2013, 2014, and 2015 were
